## Purchaser rights (summary)

When you purchase the Coltex Dataset, you receive a license to:

- Use the Dataset for lawful commercial and internal purposes
- Build and sell software, AI applications, and RAG services powered by the Dataset
- Modify the Dataset and create derivative works (subject to EULA restrictions)
- Generate embeddings, indexes, and graph databases
- Share derivative outputs with your customers (not raw Dataset redistribution)

See [EULA.md](../EULA.md) for complete permitted and restricted uses.

